Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we last\Nwore these uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kagami-{\i1}san{\i0}, Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you, {\i1}kyaran{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}...\NYour ribbon is tied crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}?\NThis is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... As of late, I am completely\Nhooked on {\i1}Mari-Mite{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mari-Mite{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Image"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't start mimicking the\Ncostumes from stuff like that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...\NThat's called cosplay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go that far, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already do a lot of that at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... Come to think of it,\Nshe works at that kind of place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}as a girl\Nin a well-to-do family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so incompatible with\Nthat image that I can't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many baseball broadcasts\Nhave run over lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are midnight anime viewers\Nthe ones forced to make the sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to watch\Nanime that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you subscribe\Nto cable or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have channels just\Nfor that and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd like to get it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys from the cable TV\Nservice said all sorts of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ending with "We can't\Nprovide service here."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem down.\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I went to treat\Nmy cavity the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you went to the dentist!\NWay to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that when you go\Nto a dentist once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to go back so many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I really know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been able to finish\Nin one or two visits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Konata-{\i1}san{\i0}. Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope nothing has occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nothing less from Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I am glad that you seem \Nfine as well, Konata-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's speaking in the same way,\Nyet it doesn't seem awkward at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, she didn't even notice\Nhow Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time that\NI've actually seen anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really greet someone else\Nwith a "Good day to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the all-girls high school\Nthat my friends attend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that they greet each other\Nwith "Good day to you" regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real well-to-do girls'\Nhigh school sure is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroi told me to collect everyone's\Nsummer vacation homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your efforts, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-Seba--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you speak of butlers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of course you would\Nassume Sebastian, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there is that image.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say something amusing, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're fresh out of vacation,\Nbut it's no time to space out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you started\Nthinking about your future
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you delve into your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the future, that means\Nafter graduation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we've passed the halfway\Npoint of our high school career.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you aren't thinking much\Nabout your future, right, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that? That's kind of rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you wanted to be in\Nthe same class as all of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you chose literary studies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tsukasa, you blabbermouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of everyone you could\Nchoose to tell, you chose her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you should just\Nbe honest and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a lonely little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! I'm here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About my summer\Nvacation homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you told me the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote answers that seemed right\Neven when I didn't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now they're making me\Ndo it over! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I help, maybe you'll have\Nto do it over yet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in all sorts of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dodging it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get an extension\Non summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the homework gets an extension?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should borrow\NKagami's notes after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last cry of a cicada\Nis like a lullaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... The extra innings forced\Nthe on-air time to shift...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there are good things\Nabout it every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the timer recording\Nis shifted wrong too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, where\Nare your glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, they broke this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had forgotten I placed them\Non top of my chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I accidentally, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but can you two lend me\Ntoday's class notes later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a clumsy girl,\Nas always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Konata's notes" "So messy that an ordinary \Nperson can't read what's written on it"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata-{\i1}san{\i0}, your handwriting \Nis so mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:51.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsukasa's notes" "So tidy that she couldn't \Nfinish copying everything down"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are useless. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we have the same teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but... Can you keep this a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would hate to pour cold water\Non their generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, let's eat lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}, Konata-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nthank you for your notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, no need for thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that I would\Nlend you my notes, Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure there\Nwon't be a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stare"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In games,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when characters in glasses\Ncome to school without glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they suddenly become\Nreally popular with guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess you don't\Nsee that in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see something\Nof that sort, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, choco-cornets\Nlook like drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drills?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it,\Nwe talked the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about which side is the head\Nof a choco-cornet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how the thin end\Nlooks more like a butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you take another look,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the thicker end looks\Nmore like the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's a fat butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And jelly rolls to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the bottom half\Nof your body gets fat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's troublesome when you're\Ntrying to buy a new skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. When you fit\Nyour waist, your hips don't fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when your hips are just right,\Nyour waist is all loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you can't help it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you buy the one with\Nthe slightly loose waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your skirt starts spinning\Naround as you walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cornet body with love handles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it to the side,\Nyou get a napping body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And too much napping gets you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cornet body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where\NI'm supposed to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, didn't you get rid of the summer\Npudginess by going on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but though I lost weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lose anything\Non my waist or my hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kagami, I can see\Nthe fruits of your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can see the difference clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that when you go on a diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the things you lose first are\Nthe things you don't need to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! You don't\Nhave to spell it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point when reading a passage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to think about the theme\Nof the sentence at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and read into what the author \Nwants to portray as a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I see..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that people with bad eyesight\Nlook like they're glaring
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and people are scared of them,\Nbut after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on the person as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked my way when\Nyou said that, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard somewhere that when\Nyou make your eyes narrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you look very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you get a look of sorrow\Nbehind the eyes or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we can't all do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late... What the\Nheck is Konata doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always complain about baseball\Ngames going into extra innings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so how can you be\Nloose about time too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, lately there\Nhave been so many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you know, maybe\NI got infected too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't catch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you late?\NDid you oversleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm not a child, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me the adult reason\Nwhy you're so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I got all ready to go out,\NI had plenty of time to spare,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I started playing\Na game to pass the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find a good place to leave it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worst excuse ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worse than a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the second\Ntrimester has lots of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the school arts festival\Nand the school sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are exams right afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky for you, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can do so well in the sports fest\Nbecause you're so athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the sports festival\Nbecause it tires me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see a homebody like you\Nin such good physical shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what our class will be\Ndoing in the arts festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we have anything\Nthat we really want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never really decide on what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we don't have someone\Nthat says, "I want to do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And usually, the first one\Nto speak ends up doing it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so nobody really says anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to get ready\Nfor all of it after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you go home so late,\Nyou miss the afternoon anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did go there after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"chicken meat - 500 grams" "celery - 2, \Nonion - 1, bell peppers - 2" "red peppers, \Ncurry powder, tomato (stewed)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm in charge of\Ncooking dinner tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What are you going to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken curry, everyone's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in our family loves chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry, huh... That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that when you let curry\Nsit overnight, it gets tastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll make a bit extra,\Nand use it for lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we'll have leftovers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hiiragi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that you, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}? What's wrong,\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curry I made last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let it sit overnight, and it rotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come? Usually curry\Ndoesn't rot in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you add something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't... But there was mold\Ngrowing on it this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have your cornet again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right because it's tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're okay with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it... I just\Nrealized this a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa and Kagami, your lunches...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes your lunches\Nhave proper side dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes you have\Nvery simple side dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a clear difference, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tsukasa and I\Ntake turns making lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm not too good\Nwith household chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, I go with the easy stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for being so simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kagami, are you the type
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:35.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Excited!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes pots explode when you try to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody like that really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, your lunch\Nlooks tasty again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I just packed\Nleftovers from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner at Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s house...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this luxurious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, these are leftovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what is this inside the fried eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the eel\Nleft over from last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I decided to put into the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you don't have\Nany eel left over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have left over is\Nmoldy chicken curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I don't think\Nyour house is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!\NThey bought me a cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my proficiency test\Nscores were unusually high...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your number.\NI'll give you mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... What was the number?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on for just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:00.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's see... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Konata, you have a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though I tend to forget it\Nat home most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, nobody but Dad\Never calls me on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the point of\Neven having a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keroro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cute? They bought me one\Ntogether with the cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me,\Nsomeone in my class
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has tons of straps hanging\Nfrom her cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when she weighed them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,apparently they weighed\Na total of 800 grams!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that many?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she took all of the straps off,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her stiff shoulders were cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, a mere phone call\Nwould be a workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know when your\Ncell phone is going to ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope someone calls me soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age, don't get\Nso excited over a cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you\Nfind your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In England, the war for\Nthe royal throne began
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between the House of Lancaster\Nand the House of York.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two houses wore red roses and\Nwhite roses when they fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so this war is called\Nthe War of the Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It began in 1455, and\Nended in 1485. At this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come pick it up at the\Nteachers' office after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad! She gave it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that you start off\Nwith a spam text message...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad? Yeah, I'm still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been talking with\NKonata and Miyuki and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it got late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine. I'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when\NI run even a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}and\Neveryone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think he'd get the idea\Nafter he calls one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fathers are always worried\Nabout their daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been more and more\Nspam lately. It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you should change\Nyour text address
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to something that isn't too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that isn't obvious?\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My address is iluvgirlsinglasses\Nin English characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have preferred\Nsomething like "maid,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but addresses like\Nmaid san and miko san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are so popular that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, hold it,\NI get what you're saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't speak so loudly\Nin front of the general public!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking with you is more\Nof a pain than the spam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell... my cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She forgot to take it out of her pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went to its reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they won't\Nbuy me a new one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the text message\Nyou sent last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one where you said Kagami\Nwanted her notes back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that was your last text message?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. By any chance, did you reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You never return text \Nmessages in a timely manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make it a point not\Nto return messages
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from someone I can\Ntalk to at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return text messages\Nwith text messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't think I needed\Nto return the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to lose friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, it's not something\Nthat needs to be rushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I didn't\Nget my notes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was reading the manga\Nthat Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}lent me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was so touched\Nthat I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, thank you for the manga!\NIt was really interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so silly that it\Ncracked you up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so touched that I cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those reactions, you two can't\Nbe talking about the same series.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. If you cry, you're in\Nthe same boat as Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you laugh, you're in\Nthe same boat as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not reading it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be classified\Nin either category!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see your reaction, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to know more about\Nyour friends... Is that so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about {\i1}Attack Number\N(One){\i0}? Do you cry, or laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is your favorite manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sgt. Frog{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two... Are they similar,\Nor are they different?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, why don't you join the\Nmanga research club or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't mind joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they have\Nvery flexible hours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw, draw, draw, draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you seriously draw all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Konata-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwho did you draw here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I could kind of tell\Nfrom the general feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so I breathe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... Kagami-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nyou're so like your image!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a frightening girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new {\i1}Full Metal {\i0}book is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the new Comp issue\Nis coming out today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to swing by Gamers.\NWanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry... I'll settle for\Nthe local bookstore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have errands to run too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you come with me to\Nnurture the friendship between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're sure\Ncoming on strong today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, the word\N"friendship" doesn't fit you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, as a sign\Nof that friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the points from\Nyour purchases...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So that's what friendship \Nis to you... That's so cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can almost reach out and get \Nthat item that I've got my eyes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she mad that I mistakenly\Nused sunflowers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the twin-tail ribbons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Towards Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}? Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's already started...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... Before\Nthey change the channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! Or so I tried to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, {\i1}Lucky Channel {\i0}has\Nstarted again this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Akira-{\i1}sama {\i0}is\Nin a very bad mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving out your own name\Nbefore the name Akira Kogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not understand\Nthe concept of rank at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that's not what...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, you've been\Ngetting needlessly popular
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all over the place with\Nthose twin-tails of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular? Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting\Na little full of yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone was expecting\Nthe Akira Fashion Project
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have {\i1}me {\i0}in twin-tails, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wear twin-drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-drills?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate\Nthe Getter's speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 2, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The days of the twin-tails are over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next fad will be twin-drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Konata say it in episode two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A drill is like an ideal for a guy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ideal, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everyone, we'll continue this\Non the radio, and on our homepage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward\Nto the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those twin-tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the ones I had?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The ones you did in live-action.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had sunflowers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen those before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:21:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How many years ago... My...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, hold on a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, was I nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very cute, and very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the first song that you sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you always get kind of nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, will my voice\Ncome out well enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like her to sing\N"Lots of Memories"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can you hand me the mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I am not used to\Ndoing something like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please forgive me if it ends up\Nbeing painful to your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Just do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cool and sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that Miyuki\Nis the connection...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:50.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Pleiades in the wind ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her singing style is cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new form of {\i1}moe{\i0}, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.32,0:23:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Where did everyone go? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:05.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Without even a send-off ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:09.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Pegasus in the meadow ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:14.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Venus in the street corner ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:19.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Where did everyone go? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:24.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Without someone looking over you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:26.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The stars on the ground ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:29.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Nobody remembers them ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:33.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ People are always staring at the sky ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:36.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the\Nnext episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, time's up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Energetic\NDespite Not Being Myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Energetic Despite Not Being Myself"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
